      static class  StoreException.Input
      Specific StoreException subtype used when the problem is with input data passed to an operation.

      Specific StoreException subtype used for problems that are due to state of store itself, and not caused by caller's actions.

      Specific StoreException subtype used for problems that are due server I/O operations, but can not be exposed as IOExceptions for some reason.
      static class  StoreException.ServerTimeout
      Specific StoreException subtype used for problems that are due to a timeout on server side.
